<h1>Hi <%= @employee.name %></h1>

<p>You are receiving this email because you have requested a password reset for your account.</p>

<h2>Please use this code to reset your password: <%= @employee.reset_password_token %> </h2>

<p>This code will expire one hour from password reset request.</p>

<h2>To reset your password please enter your code in the form here: http://localhost:3000/api/v1/password/reset</h2>

<p>If you did not request your password to be reset please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is.</p>
